name: Negative Embed
description:
NegativeEmbed

Trained on stuff only your grandather would find in his gene pool.

(Not really it's just trained on things that frankly weren't worth using for an output image.. like things SD loves to mess up)

It's not PERFECT, it's a best to be combined with other negative embeds.. as this is literally our first.

Two versions: One at 500 steps and one final at 1000 steps, this sucker took 6 hours on a free roll of Colab. BE NICE TO ME IF IT EATS YOU!

As always with NEGATIVE embeddings you stick this in the NEGATIVE PROMPT.

SAMPLE IMAGES FROM THE OUTPUTS THAT ARENT NSFW ARE INCLUDE IN THE IMAGE GALLERY - DO NOT ASK FOR THE NSFW, I WILL ASK YOU FOR MONEY, AND IF YOU HAVE NO LIFE LOL (Unless you want to train it on the data that it output)

I am not responsible for your brain dead pranks in the positive prompt.

Stuff your little brother probably finds on 4ch for free.

SAMPLE PROMPT AND RANDOM OUTPUT IMAGE:
a large painting of multicolored hair, 1girl, green eyes, open mouth, looking at viewer, green hair,a woman with colorful hair and makeup is wearing a skull and crossbones headpiece and a skull and crossbone necklace, blurry foreground, photo \(medium\), depth of field, pink hair, tattoo, blurry, solo, rainbow hair, blurry background, motion blur, art by NegativeEmbed

That's the kind of prompt it gave, not that i'm saying you should use that.

That's an output from the embed training, not me trying to prompt it to get better stuff.
